{"tid":1681313,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「橋唔怕舊」一招解決行動post推唔返上去","createTime":"2019-10-29T10:35:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T11:57:39.000Z","uid":104980,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"548fbaa8092a85618020f9fa135c91e9253769f2","tid":1681313,"uid":104980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:35:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">就係覆乜野post都好 加返句「112 維園見」/「香港人 睇日程表」</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n點解亂世中唔可以玩膠？點解唔可以做下神探？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解唔可以post下開心野？<br />\n<br />\n只係因為三毛係度帶風向 利用熱門個機制令到有用post或者行動post沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但唔代表有行動post就容唔下其他post <br />\n<br />\n三毛可以用正負皮瀏覽次數時間去集中火力洗版 但歸根究底佢地只係佔少數 唔同連登仔一人一篤口水都侵鳩死佢地<br />\n<br />\n行動post既其中一作用就係文宣 但其實要發揮文宣最大作用唔係靠個標題 而係全民皆兵 <br />\n<br />\n當每個post入面個回覆都寫住「112 維園見」一方面做到宣傳效果 另一方面就算玩緊膠係提醒緊自己係抗爭緊<br />\n<br />\n所以點樣解決呢個問題？就係你自己身上開始做起 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇藉口 唔好賴其他野"},{"pid":"269484224020af58b821147a6e9ece82c4f35c49","tid":1681313,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:36:44.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ba4e6f02c4f1c8ce2d4f64526f48d1c877c0f5f","tid":1681313,"uid":104980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:36:53.000Z","msg":"112維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8b04c90ec42daa3b69c595ac2de93706bf0928","tid":1681313,"uid":104980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:44:37.000Z","msg":"日程表啊<img src=\"/assets/f